phrases: You could have let me know if you had other plans.
Why do you think I gave you a cellphone?
You can drop me off here.
What are you going to do out here so late?
I am not planning to do anything rash.
What the heck is he doing out here?
I am pretty sure it is this way.
This is the same place as earlier.
It is my fault for saying we should go exploring...
Let us focus on finding a way back.
I learned this in science class.
The side with moss growing on it is north.
Moss always grows where the sun does not shine much!
If we walk this way, we will get to the river.
Then we can get back to where we were barbecuing.
Do you remember how you lost?
I hope you did not suffer any brain damage.
I am so glad you are okay.
I am not sure why, but we cannot use our powers in this room.
It was futile, no matter how many times I tried.
Usually, it would be easy for me to bust a hole into this wall.
What can your little brother do?
Unlike me, who cannot do anything without psychic powers,
he can figure anything out and solve any problem.
You are proud of him, huh?
So much so that you rely on him.
You will not even let me apologize.
Your sealed room is amazing as usual, Sakurai-kun.
Are we going to make those intruders a new part of the upper echelon?
First, we need to brainwash them thoroughly.
Hey, hold on a second, you guys.
Are you planning to turn decent talent into junk?
That group of middle schoolers will be recruited to HQ.
I call all the shots in the 7th Division, including personnel decisions.
I am going to take them, especially the kid in the uniform.
He will be a great friend.
Quit acting like you are more than a temp trainee.
Oh, do not get so mad.
Are you actually upset about your coworkers being defeated?
Apparently, you guys got along better than I thought.
Everyone at HQ hates one another.
Hey, what are you guys talking about?
Do not move, you suspicious jerk!
I ran out of business cards.
We have nothing to say to some weird outsider!
I am usually informed when something happens,
but I have not heard anything.
So, let me get straight to the point.
Can you all use psychic powers?
H-How does he know about that?
Sorry, but I am getting nowhere with you guys.
I am only here to talk about work with my subordinate.
Everyone here is the 7th Division Leader's subordinate.
But Division Leader Ishiguro is a direct subordinate of the boss...
I-I am going to be killed!
Surely you guys have a break room.
He totally exudes a superior aura...
It is got to be him!
He is come back to Japan!
The boss is here from HQ.
But he said he would be coming next month.
It is either an intruder or an escapee!
Hey, do not be violent to kids.
No, I am not that important.
The real deal does not brag to children.
Looks like we might actually be able to get through to him.
Um, we were suddenly kidnapped and held captive here.
Our friend is still in custody.
Were you guys really doing that?
But we were just following orders...
Not to mention, it is not right to commit villainy
just because you were ordered to.
When underlings get too obedient, they are nothing but trash.
Even if you are able to rise to the top like that,
all you will see when you look down is the filth you left in your wake.
I am not sure what you are trying to do,
but getting to the top only feels good when you do it the right way!
We have been doing such petty things...
I guess the boss would be in a league of his own.
Have you thought of anything, Ritsu?
It is probably best we do not try anything right now.
They will come check on us for sure.
Let us conserve our energy until then.
The moment we get our powers back will be the decisive moment.
We can count on your strength, too, right, Little Brother?
It is my fault for involving you two.
I will do what I can.
Hey, I was almost burned to death.
But, well, if you get serious,
the two of us will not even have to fight.
And they are moving in a pack, as always.
What the heck are you doing in a place like this?
Oh, your little brother's here, too.
Do you know the Kageyama brothers?
Do not talk that way to the boss!
What are you doing here, Master?
Th-That is Kageyama-kun's master and Claw's boss?
We are being held here against our will!
Why do you have them trapped in here?
Did he really manage to fool them?
Anyway, let us get out of here.
You should at least wait for Division Leader Ishiguro...
I am Ishiguro, the 7th Division Leader of the psychic association, Claw.
The greatest psychic in modern history, Reigen Arataka-sama.
you had the nerve to disregard me and call yourself the boss...
What are you talking about, you shrimp?
I will take care of you with my green belt in Shorinji Kenpo with a snap
Master, you are a spirit specialist.
You have gathered some efficient pawns.
If you gather enough, you might actually be able to oppose Claw.
At that angle, we will die, too!
That guy's your boss, is not he?
All of you, hide in some rooms!
If you want to make it big, you cannot die here!
This is your chance to be freed from the shackles of this black organization.
Leave this to my student and go!
Actually, I will be going, too...
There are seriously espers other than Mob?
I am no match for that power...
Actually, they are pretty difficult for me, too.
I will take care of him.
I am pretty sure he is never met anyone stronger than him yet.
Sadly, you will not get anywhere close to me...
You are not bad, being able to resist my powers.
Why do not we increase the gravity a bit?
This is one of Reigen's special moves,
where he dropkicks an esper as hard as he can.
Are you planning on fighting these guys with your psychic powers?
Did not I tell you that it is dangerous to use them against others?
Are you going to break the rule?
He had a rule like that?
In order to save me, he had no choice!
Confronting others is the hardest thing for him,
Watching you guys bully a kid who is so awkward and gets easily discouraged
definitely does not make me feel good.
Then, are you going to fight instead?
Guys, let me tell you something...
You are not supposed to harm others.
But if you are not going to listen, I will fight you.
Due to my position as their temporary guardian,
I am not going to let them fight.
I will fight you, as peacefully as possible.
First, let us see what you have got.
I will show you my hypnosis!
Look at this five yen coin.
I do not sense anything from him.
So he actually is an esper?
If this is a ruse, it is going to be dangerous.
This is one of Reigen's special moves, where he suddenly punches his opponent.
Those were not special powers at all.
That is a really sharp katana!
This is actually a toy sword made out of plastic,
but after wearing it and cursing it over the years,
Do you think you can handle my little evil spirits that I have nurtured?
I can freely exit my physical body,
and I can even clone my ethereal form.
Come on, you are dealing with children.
Maybe I will get a little angry.
Let the varying gravity from them rip you apart.
I was going to try to reason with them while they were panicked from being hit,
but I just pissed them off!
Reigen was very confident in defeating others in arguments.
He had never lost to anyone in an argument, no matter who they were.
But that is only when I am actually dealing with adults.
These brutes who are actually seriously attacking middle school kids...
These guys who are seriously talking about taking over the world...
are children who failed to grow up.
How did they end up like this?
Mob, we are getting outta here!
While I do not like the idea of being sucked into a black hole,
do not rip my body apart by pulling too hard!
You can blow them away with psychic powers?
I am surprised you were able to dodge that.
There are some weirdos back there.
If they were evil spirits, I would be able to exorcise them...
I guess you can just exorcise them.
You can wreak as much havoc as you would like today!
We are getting out of here.
Do not bother with them, Mob!
Kageyama-kun, use all of your powers!
I am an adult, so I will deal with them!
Mob, there is no need for you to stoop to their level!
Nii-san's the only one that stands a chance anymore!
We have to fight power with power!
At this rate, we are all going to die!
We just need to run away!
There is no way for us to run while dealing with their fierce attacks!
Use the powers you used back then!
Do not go head-on with someone who has murderous intent, Mob!
All four of you are going to hell.
I cannot let them all die.
I have no choice but to fight with all I have got.
If I can protect them, I do not care what happens to my opponents!
You are the one who is going to suffer in the end.
When things go south, it is okay to run away!
I came here because I saw your sign.
Er... Oh, it is just a kid.
There are times when I cannot control my powers very well,
Did someone tell you to come here and tell me that?
I have not been able to talk to anyone about this.
I thought you might be the same as me...
If I tried, I could see spirits, too.
I was troubled a lot when I was a kid, too.
Just because you have psychic powers
does not make you any less human.
It is the same as people who are fast, people who are book smart,
and people with strong body odor.
Psychic powers are just another characteristic.
You must embrace that as a part of yourself and continue to live positively.
The truth behind one's charm is kindness.
May I come to talk to you again?
Yeah, I do not know about that.
I am pretty busy, you know?
Anyway, you should go home for tod Hot!
You said you could see ghosts, too, right?
Do you know how to exorcise them, too?
Come again tomorrow around the same time.
I will show you how to use your powers.
Watching the finale in real time is an excellent decision.
